Hub version 03.01.002
=====================

INSTALLATION
------------

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES
------------

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

File::Copy                    v2.08
Scalar::Util                  v1.14
Compress::Zlib                v1.41
IO::Zlib                      v1.04
IO::File                      v1.11
Fcntl                         v1.05
Time::HiRes                   v1.66
Exporter                      v5.58
Carp                          v1.04
Archive::Tar                  v1.26
File::stat                    v1.00
Cwd                           v3.05

